<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>clean as a new pin • clean as a whistle</xh5><p> <i>clean as a new pin—</i>spotlessly clean; very tidy: He was always glad to see me in the galley which he kept as <u>clean as a new pin</u>.</p><p> <i>clean as a whistle—</i>1. <i>= clean as a new pin:</i> It was not long before the dismal little boarded-up house was as <u>clean as a whistle</u>. <i>2. </i>said of smth. neatly and skillfully done: The dog jumped through the hoop as <u>clean as a whistle</u>.</p> </entry>
